precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign an AGREEMENT
with the SWISS CONFEDERATION for the AVOIDANCE of DOUBLE TAXATION and the
PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION with respect to TAXES ON INCOME, or (b) to
issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing either the Hon. Arthur C.
Eggleton, Francis Leblanc, or Réjean Frenette to sign the said Agreement.
